    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Be prepared for any situation with the ASR Outdoor Clip Point Pocket Knife! This pocket knife features a spring assisted clip blade constructed of durable 440 stainless steel. The blade itself is 3mm thick so it can be trusted for heavy duty use. The handle has a comfortable ergonomic grip to prevent slippage, and features a majestic Bald Eagle design. This knife also comes with a window punch and seat belt cutter as an added safety measure. The metal pocket clip will allow you to easily secure the blade while not in use. This is a great every day use tool or gift idea for knife collectors and fanatics!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Clip Point Emergency Folding Pocket Knife 5&quot; American Legacy Graphic</h2>\n  <p>Be prepared for any situation with the ASR Outdoor Clip Point Pocket Knife!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>DURABLE 440 Stainless Steel Construction - Will Not Rust</li>\n    <li>CLIP POINT Pocket Knife Sturdy &amp; Sharp Blade - 5&quot; | 8.75&quot; Overall Length</li>\n    <li>BALD EAGLE Design Handle with Pocket Clip for Easy Storage When Not In Use</li>\n    <li>WINDOW PUNCH &amp; SEAT BELT CUTTER For Added Safety</li>\n    <li>ERGONOMIC Handle with Spring Assist Thumb Button</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/tools/folding_knives/KFD20024-1_bald_eagle_knife_stock1.jpg\" alt=\"Be prepared for any situation with the ASR Outdoor Clip Point Pocket Knife\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASROPK5INBALEAG</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 060886583509</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 5 in</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This pocket knife features a spring assisted clip blade constructed of durable 440 stainless steel. The blade itself is 3mm thick so it can be trusted for heavy duty use. The handle has a comfortable ergonomic grip to prevent slippage, and features a majestic Bald Eagle design.</p>\n  <p>This knife also comes with a window punch and seat belt cutter as an added safety measure. The metal pocket clip will allow you to easily secure the blade while not in use. This is a great every day use tool or gift idea for knife collectors and fanatics!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
